{
  "id": "feature-perf-002-lucide-icon-optimization",
  "title": "Eliminate Full Lucide-React Library Import (~200-400KB Savings)",
  "category": "Performance",
  "description": "## Problem\nMultiple components import the ENTIRE lucide-react library using `import * as LucideIcons from 'lucide-react'`. This imports all 1,400+ icons (~200-400KB gzipped) even though only a handful are used at any time. This is one of the single largest contributors to bundle bloat.\n\n## Current Behavior\nThe following files use `import * as LucideIcons from 'lucide-react'`:\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/board-view.tsx` (line 39)\n- `apps/ui/src/components/layout/top-nav-bar.tsx` (line 4)\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/dashboard-view.tsx` (line 30)\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/agent-view/components/session-selector.tsx` (line 13)\n- `apps/ui/src/components/ui/icon-picker.tsx` (line 3)\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/settings-view/components/edit-project-dialog.tsx` (line 14)\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/settings-view/projects/projects-section.tsx` (line 24)\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/board-view/dialogs/add-feature-dialog.tsx` (line 61)\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/board-view/components/agent-chat-panel.tsx` (line 15)\n\nThe pattern is used to dynamically render project icons by name:\n```typescript\nif (project?.icon && project.icon in LucideIcons) {\n  return (LucideIcons as unknown as Record<string, LucideIcon>)[project.icon];\n}\n```\n\n## Required Changes\n1. Create a curated icon map (`apps/ui/src/lib/icon-registry.ts`) with only the ~50-80 icons that are offered in the icon picker, plus commonly used UI icons\n2. Replace all `import * as LucideIcons` with imports from the curated registry\n3. Update `icon-picker.tsx` to use the curated list instead of the full library\n4. For any component that just renders a project icon by name, use the registry lookup\n5. Keep individual named imports (e.g., `import { Search, Plus } from 'lucide-react'`) as these ARE tree-shakeable\n\n## Pattern to Follow\n```typescript\n// apps/ui/src/lib/icon-registry.ts\nimport { Folder, FolderCode, Code, Star, Rocket, ... } from 'lucide-react';\nimport type { LucideIcon } from 'lucide-react';\n\nexport const ICON_REGISTRY: Record<string, LucideIcon> = {\n  Folder, FolderCode, Code, Star, Rocket, ...\n};\n\nexport function getProjectIcon(iconName: string | undefined): LucideIcon | null {\n  if (!iconName) return null;\n  return ICON_REGISTRY[iconName] ?? null;\n}\n\nexport const AVAILABLE_ICON_NAMES = Object.keys(ICON_REGISTRY);\n```\n\n## Files to Modify\n- Create: `apps/ui/src/lib/icon-registry.ts` - Curated icon map\n- `apps/ui/src/components/ui/icon-picker.tsx` - Use curated list instead of full import\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/board-view.tsx` - Replace `* as LucideIcons`\n- `apps/ui/src/components/layout/top-nav-bar.tsx` - Replace `* as LucideIcons`\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/dashboard-view.tsx` - Replace `* as LucideIcons`\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/agent-view/components/session-selector.tsx` - Replace `* as LucideIcons`\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/settings-view/components/edit-project-dialog.tsx` - Replace `* as LucideIcons`\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/settings-view/projects/projects-section.tsx` - Replace `* as LucideIcons`\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/board-view/dialogs/add-feature-dialog.tsx` - Replace `* as LucideIcons`\n- `apps/ui/src/components/views/board-view/components/agent-chat-panel.tsx` - Replace `* as LucideIcons`\n\n## Expected Impact\n- Bundle size reduction of 200-400KB (gzipped)\n- Faster parsing and execution on initial load\n- Icon picker still works but with a curated, sensible subset\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- No `import * as LucideIcons` anywhere in the codebase\n- Icon picker shows all available project icons from the curated registry\n- Project icons display correctly throughout the app\n- Bundle analyzer confirms lucide-react chunk is dramatically smaller\n- All existing icon selections continue to work (backward compatible)",
